'''本諾·施米茨'''（{{lang-de|Benno Schmitz}}；{{bd|1994年|12月17日}}）是一位[[德國|德國]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是右後衛。他現在效力於[[德甲|德甲]]球隊[[科隆足球俱乐部|科隆]]<ref name="soccerway">{{cite web|url=http://int.soccerway.com/players/benno-schmitz/215597/|title=Germany - B. Schmitz - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway|publisher=soccerway.com|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-date=2017-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109211738/http://int.soccerway.com/players/benno-schmitz/215597/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也代表德國U20國家隊參賽<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dfb.de/u-20-maenner/spiele-termine/spielplan/?spieledb_path=%2Fteams%2F31140%2Fnational_player%2F233581 | title = U 20-Männer: Spielerprofil Benno Schmitz | trans-title = Men's U20: Player's profile Benno Schmitz | language = de | publisher = dfb.de | date = 7 May 2014 | accessdate = 30 August 2014 | archive-date = 2014-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140905101422/http://www.dfb.de/u-20-maenner/spiele-termine/spielplan/?spieledb_path=%2Fteams%2F31140%2Fnational_player%2F233581 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

